bha%20in%202008%2C%20where%20it%20was%20passed%20in%202010.%20However%2C%20it%20never%20reached%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20for%20consideration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20historic%20women's%20quota%20bill%20which%20proposes%20a%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20Parliament%20and%20state%20legislatures%2C%20may%20not%20come%20into%20effect%20until%202029.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20women's%20quota%20can%20only%20be%20implemented%20after%20the%20first%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%20following%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20occur%20in%202027%2C%20as%20delimitation%20is%20only%20conducted%20after%20the%20next%20census.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20potential%20delay%20has%20provided%20fodder%20to%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20who%20have%20demanded%20an%20urgent%20implementation%20of%20the%20bill%20with%20a%20sub-quota%20for%20OBCs.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOpening%20the%20debate%20in%20Parliament%20yesterday%2C%20Congress%20parliamentary%20party%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%2013%20years%2C%20Indian%20women%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20their%20political%20responsibilities%2C%20and%20now%20they%20are%20being%20asked%20to%20wait%20for%20a%20few%20more%20years%20--%20two%20years%2C%20four%20years%2C%20six%20years%2C%20eight%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTwo%20things%20seem%20strange.%20One%2C%20the%20Idea%20that%20you%20need%20new%20census%20for%20this%20bill%20and%20new%20delimitation%20and%20I%20think%20this%20bill%20can%20be%20implemented%20today.%20I%20wonder%20this%20is%20not%20designed%20to%20push%20it%20forward%20by%20seven%20or%20eight%20years%20and%20let%20it%20play%20out%20the%20way%20it%20does.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20that%20both%20delimitation%20and%20census%20will%20begin%20after%20the%20next%20general%20election.%20%26quot%3BLet%20us%20rise%20above%20partisan%20politics%20to%20give%20women%20the%20respect%20they%20deserve.%20Earlier%20they%20have%20been%20left%20disappointed%20four%20times%20by%20Parliament.%20Let%20this%20bill%20be%20passed%20unanimously%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20hailed%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20bill%20with%20overwhelming%20support%2C%20thanking%20MPs%20across%20party%20lines%20for%20their%20vote.%20%26quot%3BI%20thank%20MPs%20across%20Party%20lines%20who%20voted%20in%20support%20of%20this%20Bill.%20The%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%20is%20a%20historic%20legislation%20which%20will%20further%20boost%20women%20empowerment%20and%20will%20enable%20even%20greater%20participation%20of%20women%20in%20our%20political%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695261000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fho7l0qc8_new-parliament-building_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-lok-sabha-test-cleared-womens-quota-bill-in-rajya-sabha-today-10-facts-4409138%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday%2C%20is%20set%20for%20another%20litmus%20test%20today%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Day%204%20of%20the%20special%20session%20of%20Parliament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-lok-sabha-test-cleared-womens-quota-bill-in-rajya-sabha-today-10-facts-4409138%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-lok-sabha-test-cleared-womens-quota-bill-in-rajya-sabha-today-10-facts-4409138%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-lok-sabha-test-cleared-w