%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202022%2C%20TikTok%20announced%20it%20was%20launching%20a%20new%20contextual-advertising%20product%20in%20which%20brands%20could%20buy%20ads%20alongside%20%26quot%3Bthe%20top%204%25%26quot%3B%20of%20content%20in%20different%20categories%20like%20fashion%2C%20cooking%2C%20and%20beauty.%20It%20agreed%20to%20split%20half%20of%20the%20revenue%20with%20the%20creator%20whose%20video%20appeared%20before%20the%20in-feed%20ad.%20Only%20creators%20with%20at%20least%20100%2C000%20followers%20qualify%20for%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-to-share-half-ad-revenue-with-creators-pulse-program-2022-5%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3Ehow%20TikTok%20Pulse%20compares%20to%20other%20ad%20revenue-sharing%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20creators%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.tiktok.com%2Fen-us%2Fpulse-premiere%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%202023%20it%20was%20also%20testing%20a%20version%20of%20the%20Pulse%20program%20for%20traditional%20media%20publishers%20called%20Pulse%20Premiere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20the%20Creator%20Fund%2C%20initial%20payments%20from%20TikTok%20Pulse%20have%20been%20underwhelming%2C%20creators%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-pulse-ad-revenue-share-payments-creators-2022-11%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Ehow%20much%20gaming%20and%20lifestyle%20creators%20have%20earned%20from%20Pulse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20creators%20who%20shared%20payment%20data%20with%20Insider%20saw%20Pulse%20RPMs%20in%20the%20%247%20to%20%248%20range%2C%20one%20creator%20reported%20an%20RPM%20closer%20to%20%243.%20The%20creator%20RPMs%20were%20competitive%20on%20TikTok%20Pulse%20when%20compared%20to%20other%20ad-revenue%20solutions%20like%20YouTube's%20partner%20program%20for%20long-form%20video%2C%20but%20the%20revenue-generating%20views%20were%20comparatively%20low%2C%20often%20dipping%20below%201%2C000%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20super%20excited%20to%20join%20it%2C%20but%20I'm%20six%20cents%20richer%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Betts%20Waller%2C%20a%20gaming%20creator%20who%20has%20around%20390%2C000%20followers%20on%20his%20TikTok%20account%20Forrest%20Dump%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaller%20only%20had%20eight%20video%20views%20qualify%20for%20Pulse%20earnings%20over%20the%20pay%20period%20between%20September%2030%20and%20October%2030%202022%2C%20despite%20posting%20videos%20that%20garnered%20tens%20of%20thousands%2C%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%2C%20and%20even%20millions%20of%20views.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20creators%20saw%20a%20similar%20pattern%20of%20Pulse-monetized%20views%20falling%20far%20below%20total%20video-view%20counts%20for%20a%20payment%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider%20that%20even%20if%20a%20user's%20video%20generates%20millions%20of%20views%2C%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20each%20video%20view%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20Pulse%20ad.%20Due%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20TikTok%20algorithm%2C%20some%20videos%20will%20contribute%20to%20more%20ad%20impressions%20than%20others%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20continuing%20to%20work%20on%20improving%20Pulse%20so%20that%20we%20can%20better%20support%20our%20creators%20and%20advertisers%2C%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20expanding%20our%20monetization%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%20rolled%20out%20a%20similar%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-revamp-creator-pay-revenue-share-shorts-tiktok-challenge-2022-9%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%20data-remove-tab-index%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-stringi