they%20saw%20their%20stock%20price%20taking%20a%20dive.%20So%20Rupert%20and%20Lachlan%20Murdoch%20said%2C%20'Oh%2C%20if%20we%20aren't%20embracing%20this%20disinformation%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20problem%2C'%26quot%3B%20Connolly%20said%20in%20court%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20they%20ordered%20their%20lieutenants%2C%20Suzanne%20Scott%20and%20Jay%20Wallace%2C%20'You're%20taking%20out%20Smartmatic%2C%20you%20are%20embracing%20this%20disinformation%20about%20voting%20machines%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20lo%20and%20behold%2C%20that's%20exactly%20what%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20Murphy%2C%20an%20attorney%20representing%20both%20Fox%20Corp.%20and%20Fox%20News%2C%20argued%20that%20it%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20show%20that%20the%20Murdochs%20were%20generally%20involved%20in%20shaping%20Fox%20News's%20editorial%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20for%20Fox%20Corp.%20to%20remain%20a%20defendant%20in%20the%20case%2C%20she%20said%2C%20Smartmatic%20would%20have%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20Murdochs%20were%20specifically%20talking%20about%20Smartmatic%C2%A0when%20they%20communicated%20with%20top%20Fox%20officials%20about%20the%20direction%20of%20news%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20a%20very%20good%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20said%20in%20court%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%2C%20they%20don't%20actually%20allege%20any%20facts%20that%20connect%20between%20the%20vast%20gulf%20between%20saying%2C%20'They%20should%20pivot%20and%20we%20should%20be%20careful%20about%20our%20messaging%2C'%20and%20then%20connecting%20it%20to%2C%20'And%20therefore%20you%20should%20say%20a%20bunch%20of%20things%20about%20Smartmatic.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESmartmatic%20says%20it%20has%20evidence%20of%20the%20Murdochs'%20involvement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmartmatic%20initially%20filed%20its%20lawsuit%20against%20Fox%20Corp.%20and%20Fox%20News%20in%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmartmatic-sues-fox-news-over-election-conspiracy-theories-2021-2%5C%22%3Earguing%20they%20defamed%20the%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20their%20hosts%20allowed%20Rudy%20Giuliani%20and%20Sidney%20Powell%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20also%20defendants%20in%20the%20case%20%E2%80%94%20to%20spout%20false%20conspiracy%20theories%20about%20how%20Smartmatic%20rigged%20the%202020%20presidential%20election%20against%20Trump%20and%20in%20favor%20of%20now-President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20network's%20motivation%20for%20pushing%20those%20theories%2C%20Smartmatic%20argued%2C%20was%20to%20fend%20off%20competition%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20Newsmax%2C%20which%20had%20more%20readily%20embraced%20those%20false%20theories%20and%20was%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20embraced%20by%20Trump%2C%20who%20held%20powerful%20sway%20over%20the%20Republican%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20defend%20this%20case%20surrounding%20extremely%20newsworthy%20events%20when%20it%20goes%20to%20trial%2C%20likely%20in%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Fox%20News%20representative%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BAs%20our%20financial%20expert's%20report%20shows%20and%20ongoing%20discovery%20has%20since%20confirmed%2C%20Smartmatic's%20damages%20claims%20are%20implausible%2C%20disconnected%20from%20reality%2C%20and%20intended%20to%20chill%20vital%20First%20Amendment%20freedoms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222948%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rupert%20lachlan%20murdoch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650b4459bf943d00195c8adf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222211%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERupert%20and%20Lachlan%20Murdoch%20at%20the%20US%20Open.%3Cp%3EJean%20Catuffe%2FGC%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDominion%2C%20another%20election%20technology%20company%20that%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20many%20of%20the%20same%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20agreed%20to%20settle%20its%20d