00%20Philadelphians%20suffered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewtrusts.org%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fassets%2F2022%2F04%2Fphiladelphia-2022-the-state-of-the-city.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efatal%20overdose%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20in%202021%2C%20the%20overdose%20death%20toll%20was%20almost%201%2C300%2C%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dea.gov%2Fengage%2Foperation-engage-philadelphia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E8%20in%2010%20fatalities%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20attributable%20to%20drugs%20laced%20with%20the%20powerful%20opioid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPublic%20health%20is%20not%20a%20field%20for%20moralizing.%20People%20should%20not%2C%20generally%2C%20inject%20into%20their%20bodies%20a%20substance%20they%20bought%20with%20cash%20from%20a%20stranger%20on%20the%20street.%20But%20people%20will%20because%20they%20are%20physically%20hooked%20on%20those%20substances.%20And%20many%20will%20not%20resort%20to%20best%20practices%2C%20like%20using%20a%20clean%20needle%2C%20and%20contract%20diseases%20that%20require%20lifelong%20treatment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKensington%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20in%20northeast%20Philadelphia%2C%20is%20ground%20zero%20for%20this%20behavior.%20It's%20home%20to%20open-air%20dealing%20in%20heroin%20and%20%26quot%3Btranq%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20animal%20sedative%20that%20can%20result%20in%20limbs%20being%20amputated.%20But%20people%20all%20over%20Philadelphia%2C%20addicted%20and%20unhoused%2C%20can%20be%20found%20lying%20motionless%20on%20sidewalks%20or%20a%20stranger's%20front%20stoop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20the%20state%20of%20things.%20Knowing%20this%2C%20and%20presumably%20being%20aware%20of%20the%20science%20%E2%80%94%20a%20supervised%20injection%20site%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada%2C%20reduced%20overdose%20deaths%20by%2035%25%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6565790%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20one%20study%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20those%20who%20used%20the%20site%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20also%20seek%20drug%20treatment%20%E2%80%94%20members%20of%20Philadelphia's%20city%20council%2C%20almost%20all%20Democrats%20who%20style%20themselves%20progressive%2C%20this%20month%20acted%20in%20near-unanimity%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inquirer.com%2Fnews%2Fphiladelphia%2Fsupervised-injection-site-ban-philadelphia-city-council-20230914.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eeffectively%20prohibit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20something%20that%20does%20not%20currently%20exist%3A%20safe%20spaces%20where%20someone%20can%20inject%20a%20drug%2C%20with%20a%20clean%20needle%2C%20in%20front%20of%20someone%20trained%20to%20address%20an%20overdose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20another%20tragic%20page%20in%20a%20tragic%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20Burris%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Center%20of%20Public%20Health%20Law%20Research%20at%20Temple%20University%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BPhiladelphia%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20come%20together%20to%20do%20something%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20done%2C%20that%20is%20backed%20by%20evidence%20and%20experience.%20It%20pushed%20a%20lot%20of%20buttons%2C%20but%20we%20should%20as%20a%20community%20%5Bhave%5D%20been%20able%20to%20talk%20it%20through%20and%20get%20to%20a%20solution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhiladelphia's%20city%20council%20did%20allow%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20site%20opening%20in%20one%20western%20district%20of%20the%20city%2C%20and%20some%20members%20suggested%20they%20were%20only%20asking%20for%20more%20community%20input%2C%20although%20cynics%20would%20note%20such%20input%20tends%20to%20be%2C%20predictably%2C%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bnot%20in%20my%20backyard%26quot%3B%20variety.%20Councilman%20Isaiah%20Thomas%2C%20who%20has%20a%20reputation%20as%20a%20progressive%2C%20likened%20supervised%20injection%20sites%20to%20billionaires%20steamrolling%20opposition%20and%20constructing%20a%20downtown%20sports%20arena%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inquirer.com%2Fnews%2Fphiladelphia%2Fsupervised-injection-site-ban-philadelphia-city-council-20230914.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Philadelphia%20Inquirer%20reported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20would%20be%20up%20in%20arms%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Driscoll%2C%20a%20Democrat%20representing%20the%20city's%20northeast%2C%20was%20adamant%20that%20he%20was%20opposing%20the%20whole%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20put%20these%20folks%20into%20compassionate%2C%20long-term%20care%20and%20get%20them%20on%20the%20road%20to%20recovery%2C%20not%20postpone%20the%20inevitable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inquirer.com%2Fnews%2Fphiladelphia%2Fsupervised-injection-site-ban-philadelphia-city-council-20230914.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Philadelphia%20Inquirer%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%2C%20most%20of%20Philly's%20elected%20Democrats%C2%A0are%20in%20an%20uneasy%20but%20very%20real%20alliance%20with%20Donald%20Trump.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20former%20president's%20Department%20of%20Justice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhyy.org%2Farticles%2Ffederal-prosecutors-sue-to-stop-nations-first-planned-supervised-injection-site-in-philly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esued%20to%20stop%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Philadelphia-based%20nonprofit%2C%20Safehouse%2C%20from%20opening%20what%20would%20have%20been%20the%20country's%20first%20safe%20injection%20site%2C%20citing%20a%20federal%20law%20originally%20aimed%20at%20crack%20houses.%20The%20Biden%20administration%20is%20looking%20to%20have%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhyy.org%2Farticles%2Fsafehouse-supervised-injection-suit-department-justice-dismiss%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecase%20dismissed%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bipartisan%20fantasy%20is%20admirable%2C%20albeit%20unfunded.%20Instead%20of%20enabling%20the%20safer%20consumption%20of%20a%20dangerous%20drug%2C%20the%20benevolent%20state%20could%20instead%20extend%20its%20iron%20hand%20to%20the%20afflicted%20user%2C%20leading%20them%20down%20the%20path%20to%20treatment%20(paying%20for%20it%2C%20even%3A%20the%20food%3B%20the%20shelter%3B%20the%20counseling)%C2%A0and%20eventual%20reintegration%20with%20society%2C%20doing%20what%20is%20best%20for%20them%2C%C2%A0whether%20they%20can%20see%20that%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trouble%2C%20according%20to%20Dr.%20Nora%20Volkow%2C%20head%20of%20the%20National%20Institute%20on%20Drug%20Abuse%2C%20is%20that%20this%20approach%20does%20not%20usually%20work%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20scaled-down%20versions%20of%20mandatory%20treatment%20that%20actually%20exist.%20%26quot%3BThe%20data%20does%20not%20show%20that%20it's%20beneficial%20to%20put%20someone%20in%20jail%20or%20prison%20or%20force%20them%20against%20their%20will%20to%20go%20to%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F04%2F30%2Fopinion%2Fforced-addiction-treatment.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eshe%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Philadelphia%2C%20a%20city%20battling%20not%20just%20drug%20addiction%20but%20poverty%20and%20gun%20violence%2C%20is%20not%20about%20to%20open%20drug%20treatment%20resorts.%20The%20stopgap%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20a%20safe%20place%20to%20inject%20drugs%20%E2%80%94%20falls%20far%20short%20of%20eliminating%20the%20scourge%20of%20drug%20addiction%20but%20exists%20just%20a%20couple%20hours%20north%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20where%20advocates%20say%20in%20just%20its%20first%20few%20months%2C%20it%20prevented%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2022%2F06%2F04%2F1103114131%2Fsupervised-injection-sites-in-nyc-have-saved-lives-but-officials-wont-provide-fu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehundreds%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20potential%20overdose%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElected%20officials%20are%20probably%20being%20honest%20when%20they%20say%20that%20most%20of%20the%20constituents%20they%20hear%20from%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20idea.%20Most%20people%20would%20rather%20a%20cute%20caf%C3%A9%20open%20up%20next%20door%20and%2C%20for%20that%2C%20maybe%20they%20should%20not%20be%20blamed.%20But%20the%20seeming%20lack%20of%20public%20support%20is%20also%20a%20product%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20few%20in%20public%20office%20have%20been%20interested%20in%20putting%20in%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERonda%20Goldfein%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Safehouse%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20AIDS%20Law%20Project%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20said%20she%20doesn't%20blame%20Philadelphians%20for%20being%20skeptical%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20they%20are%20perhaps%20so%20angry%2C%20understandably%2C%20because%20the%20city%20has%20failed%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldfein%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20residents%20who%20have%20seen%20public%20drug%20use%20extend%20across%20the%20city%2C%20opening%20a%20safe%20injection%20site%20may%20sound%20like%20opening%20a%20Walmart%20Supercenter%20for%20narcotics%20%E2%80%94%20another%20boneheaded%20solution%20imposed%20by%20a%20negligent%20city%20government%20that%20will%20only%20attract%20more%20of%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20that%20what%20angers%20many%20residents%20the%20most%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0people%20doing%20drugs%20in%20public%2C%20from%20the%20subway%20to%20the%20alley%20behind%20their%20home%2C%20leaving%20needles%20in%20the%20reach%20of%20pets%20and%20children%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0is%20just%20what%20safe%20injection%20sites%20are%20intended%20to%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20take%20it%20all%20inside%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Goldfein%20puts%20it.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20offering%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%20they're%20complaining%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhiladelphia%20Mayor%20Jim%20Kenney%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20public%20officials%20to%20explicitly%20endorse%20supervised%20injection%20sites.%20He%20leaves%20office%20in%20a%20few%20months%2C%20and%20his%20likely%20Democratic%20successor%2C%20Cherelle%20Parker%2C%20has%20already%20endorsed%20the%20city%20council's%20de%20facto%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20council's%20veto-proof%20decision%2C%20Kenney%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhyy.org%2Farticles%2Fphiladelphia-mayor-jim-kenny-supervised-injection-site-ban-overdose-deaths%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%20reporters%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20opponents%20would%20have%20blood%20on%20their%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20really%20want%20to%20say%20that%20you%20want%20to%20fix%20this%20problem%20or%20address%20this%20problem%2C%20then%20address%20it%2C%20and%20stop%20trying%20to%20put%20your%20head%20in%20the%20sand%20and%20say%20this%20doesn't%20work%20%E2%80%94%20because%20it%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20Kenney%20told%20reporters.%20It%20works%20in%20Canada%20and%20Europe%2C%20he%20said%3B%20it%20works%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20%26quot%3BIf%20%5Bcity%5D%20council%20wants%20to%20continue%20to%20avoid%20this%20and%20resist%20it%2C%20it's%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20Kenney%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20it%20means%20you're%20gonna%20have%20people%20dying%20as%20a%20result%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20news%20tip%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acdavis%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ecdavis%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphiladelphia-kensington-supervised-injection-sites-heroin-fentanyl-opioid-epidemic-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A16952401860