status%2F1704445571249950982%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSee%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20so-called%20expert%20panel.%20The%20unfortunate%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20is%20being%20politicised%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20to%20defame%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20army%20officer%20who%20retired%20after%2040%20years%20of%20service%20-%20including%20in%20the%20Intelligence%20Corps%20-%20told%20NDTV%20on%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20members%20of%20the%20Geneva%20panel%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%20are%20Reem%20Alsalem%2C%20UN%20special%20rapporteur%20on%20violence%20against%20women%20and%20girls%3B%20Florence%20N%20Lowe%2C%20head%20of%20North%20American%20Manipur%20Tribal%20Association%3B%20Henna%20Zuberi%2C%20advocacy%20director%20of%20Justice%20for%20All%2C%20and%20Nury%20Turkel%2C%20commissioner%20of%20the%20US%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%2C%20who%20sent%20a%20pre-recorded%20video%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Evangelical%20Alliance%20said%20Manipur%20has%20been%20seeing%20large-scale%20violence%20%26quot%3Bprimarily%20against%20the%20tribal%20Christian%20Zo%20people%20(Kuki%2C%20Zomi%2C%20Hmar%20tribes)%20that%20led%20to%20at%20least%20180%20deaths%2C%20rampant%20sexual%20violence%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20churches%20and%20thousands%20of%20homes%20that%20were%20demolished%20or%20burned%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fro94jndg_churachandpur_625x300_08_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhuraijam%20Athouba%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Core%20Committee%20(COCOMI)%2C%