0who%20moderated%20the%20discussion%2C%20then%20insisted%20that%20the%20session%20has%20to%20end%20and%20offered%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20COCOMI%20spokesperson%20after%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20allow%20me%20to%20speak.%20Let%20the%20audience%20know.%20Why%20are%20we%20completely%20neglecting%20the%20issue%20of%20narcoterrorism%3F%20The%20UNODC%20has%20already%20reported%20Churachandpur%20has%20become%20the%20hub%20of%20the%20new%20Golden%20Triangle...%20It%20is%20a%20completely%20one-sided%20discussion.%20It%20should%20be%20neutral%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Athouba%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20Office%20on%20Drugs%20and%20Crime.%20The%20%26quot%3BGolden%20Triangle%26quot%3B%20refers%20to%20the%20tri-junction%20of%20the%20Myanmar%2C%20Laos%20and%20Thailand%20borders%2C%20which%20used%20to%20be%20the%20preferred%20route%20of%20drug%20traffickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20al-Saliby%20strongly%20denied%20it%20was%20a%20one-sided%20discussion.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20a%20one-sided%20discussion.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20we%20can%20provide%20after%20the%20discussion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20you%20should%20have%20the%20patience%20to%20listen%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Athouba%20shot%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20broke%20out%20in%20Churachandpur%20district%20on%20May%203%20amid%20a%20protest%20by%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20over%20the%20Meiteis'%20demand%20for%20inclusion%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20category.%20Thousands%20from%20both%20communities%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced%20and%20nearly%20200%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20forces%20have%20set%20up%20safe%20zones%20between%20Meitei-%20and%20Kuki-dominated%20areas%20to%20prevent%20escalation%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695237720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F2v4hsppg_manipur-violence-_625x3