ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Ff-35-fighter-jet-missing-pilot-ejects-mishap-rcna105534%5C%22%3Etold%20NBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20jet%20was%20left%20in%20autopilot%20mode%20and%20may%20have%20remained%20airborne%20for%20some%20time%2C%20though%20they%20later%20said%20they%20didn't%20know%20for%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20were%2C%20however%2C%20sure%20the%20aircraft%20was%20down%20as%20of%20midday%20Monday%2C%20and%20a%20few%20hours%20later%2C%20officials%20confirmed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmissing-f35-jet-found-debris-crash-pilot-ejected-training-mishap-2023-9%5C%22%3Edebris%20field%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20discovered%20in%20Williamsburg%20County%20about%20two%20hours%20northeast%20of%20Joint%20Base%20Charleston.%20%26quot%3BThe%20mishap%20is%20currently%20under%20investigation%2C%20and%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20provide%20additional%20details%20to%20preserve%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20investigative%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added%20in%20a%20press%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20of%20the%20specifics%20remain%20under%20wraps%20or%20are%20perhaps%20simply%20still%20unknown%20at%20this%20time%2C%20there's%20a%20chance%20a%20feature%20specific%20to%20the%20Marine%20Corps'%20F-35B%20model%20could've%20played%20a%20role%20in%20how%20and%20when%20the%20pilot%20ejected.%20With%20the%20auto-eject%20system%2C%C2%A0it%20might%20have%20been%20involuntary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22F-35B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F55a9ccbc2acae78b0e8b7b1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20U.S.%20Marine%20F-35B%20Lightning%20II%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighters%20complete%20vertical%20landings%20aboard%20the%20USS%20Wasp%20(LHD-1)%20during%20operational%20testing%20May%2018%2C%202015.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FU.S.%20Marine%20Corps%2FLance%20Cpl.%20Remington%20Hall%2FHandout%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20in%20function%20to%20the%20Harrier%20jump%20jet%2C%20the%20B%20variant%20of%20the%20F-35%20Lightning%20II%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter%20is%20a%20short%20takeoff%2Fvertical%20landing%20model.%20It%20features%20a%20unique%20auto-eject%20capability%20and%20is%20the%20first%20US%20aircraft%20to%20do%20so%2C%20and%20it%20was%20included%20for%20a%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35Bs%20used%20by%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20can%20hover%20kind%20of%20like%20a%20helicopter%2C%20which%20is%20a%20beneficial%20capability%20for%20use%20aboard%20amphibious%20assault%20ships%20and%20on%20airfields%20with%20short%20runways.%20It%20does%20this%20using%C2%A0a%20large%20lift%20fan%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20jet's%20fuselage.%20If%20that%20fan%20were%20to%20fail%2C%20or%20power%20from%20the%20engine%20were%20to%20cut%20out%2C%20it's%20possible%20the%20jet%20could%20flip%20over%20and%20fall%20faster%20than%20a%20pilot%20could%20react%20to%20either%20stabilize%20the%20aircraft%20or%20eject%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20dangerous%20situation%20for%20the%20pilot%20and%20aircraft%2C%20the%20auto-eject%20would%20likely%20activate%2C%20although%20the%20parameters%20for%20this%20function%20are%20unknown.%C2%A0All%20that's%20clear%20is%20that%20the%20Martin-Baker%20US16E%20ejection%20seat%20can%20be%20automatically%20engaged%20without%20pilot%20input.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20December%202022%20when%2C%20during%20a%20test%20flight%20at%20Naval%20Air%20Station%20Joint%20Reserve%20Base%20Fort%20Worth%20in%20Texas%2C%20an%20F-35B%20was%20hovering%20above%20the%20runway%20before%20suddenly%20dropping%2C%20bouncing%2C%20jerking%20forward%2C%20and%20then%20slamming%20into%20the%20runway%20nose-first.%20The%20hard%20impact%20caused%20the%20F-35B%20to%20spin%20around%20and%20smoke%20before%20the%20pilot%20ejected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20possible%20that%2C%20had%20the%20aircraft%20rolled%20over%20in%20a%20different%20direction%2C%20the%20pilot%20wouldn't%20have%20enough%20time%20or%20space%20to%20eject%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%20%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FUdSVMgay0MI%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20currently%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20F-35's%20auto-eject%20safety%20mechanism%20influenced%20Sunday's%20incident%20and%20when%20or%20how%20the%20pilot%20ejected%20from%20the%20plane%C2%A0beyond%20what%20an%20anonymous%20official%20told%20the%20AP.%20The%20results%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20which%20could%20still%20be%20months%20away%2C%20will%20reveal%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20B%20variant%2C%20there%20is%20also%20the%20F-35A%20conventional%20takeoff%20and%20landing%20variant%20designed%20for%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20and%20the%20F-35C%20carrier%20variant%20made%20for%20both%20the%20Navy%20and%20Marine%20Corps.%20The%20variants%20have%20different%20features%20that%20allow%20%26quot%3Bmilitary%20forces%20to%20achieve%20service-specific%20mission%20capability%2C%20while%20still%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20economies%20of%20scale%20that%20result%20from%20the%20parts%20and%20processes%20that%20are%20common%20to%20all%20three%20variants%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20jet's%20manufacturer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lockheedmartin.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Flockheed-martin%2Faero%2Fdocuments%2FF-35%2Ff35-brochure.pdf%5C%22%3ELockheed%20Martin%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter%20is%20a%20highly%20advanced%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20aircraft%20known%20for%20high-end%20capabilities%20and%20stealth.%20They%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2021%2F03%2F05%2Fadam-smith-f35%2F%5C%22%3Eexceptionally%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20single%20F-35B%20estimated%20to%20cost