ted%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9Cany%20allegations%20like%20this%20should%20be%20troubling%20to%20anyone%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20with%20an%20active%20criminal%20investigation%2C%20I%20hope%20that%20we%20can%20make%20sure%20that%20perpetrators%20are%20brought%20to%20justice%20and%20that%20we%20can%20all%20allow%20the%20space%20for%20that%20information%20and%20that%20investigation%20to%20occur%20before%20anybody%20leaps%20to%20judgment.%20And%20to%20me%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20most%20important%20role%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Garcetti.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20underlined%20that%20to%20%E2%80%9Ceach%20one%20of%20us%2C%20sovereignty%20is%20a%20very%20important%20principle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20US%20could%20mediate%20in%20this%20diplomatic%20spat%2C%20he%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cway%20too%20early.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20certainly%20have%20a%20deep%20respect%20and%20huge%20agenda%20and%20relationship%20here.%20And%20us%20having%20a%20relationship%20speaks%20for%20itself.%20We%20share%20our%20border%20we%20share%20so%20much%20history%20and%20culture%20together%20and%20the%20values.%20I%20think%2C%20for%20us%2C%20it%20is%20critical%20for%20us%20to%20return%20the%20three%20principles%20%E2%80%93%20sovereignty%2C%20non-interference%20to%20allow%20the%20criminal%20justice%20investigations%20to%20be%20carried%20out%2C%20And%20then%20there%E2%80%99ll%20be%20accountability%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20another%20query%20whether%20there%20was%20a%20mismatch%20between%20India%20and%20the%20West%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20democratic%20principles%20and%20incitement%20of%20violence%2C%20the%20US%20envoy%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20take%20the%20safety%20of%20Indian%20diplomats%20seriously.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20added%20that%20violence%20is%20not%20freedom%20of%20expression.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695230454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F07103531%2FF0XfRHUWAAo8zAP.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-calls-on-india-join-canada-investigation-nijjar-killing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20White%20House%20also%20denied%20a%20media%20report%20which%20claimed%20that%20the%20US%20had%20rebuffed%20a%20Canadian%20proposal%20for%20a%20joint%20statement%20from%20its%20allies%20on%20the%20Indian%20government's%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20murder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-calls-on-india-join-canada-investigation-nijjar-killing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20Tourist%20Climbing%20'Stairway%20To%20Heaven'%20Falls%20300%20Feet%20To%20His%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20British%20tourist%20died%20after%20he%20plunged%20more%20than%2090%20meters%20to%20his%20death%20while%20scaling%20a%20narrow%20ladder%20on%20an%20Austrian%20mountain%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2023%2F09%2F20%2Faustria-british-tourist-dies-after-falling-from-stairway-to-heaven-19527563%2F%5C%22%3EMetro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0This%20area%20is%20popular%20among%20tourists%20seeking%20picturesque%20Instagram%20photos.%20The%20aerial%20ladder%2C%20known%20locally%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bstairway%20to%20heaven%26quot%3B%20rises%20sharply%20in%20the%20Dachstein%20Mountains%20outside%20of%20Salzburg.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tragic%20incident%20happened%20on%20September%2012%20when%20the%2042-year-old%C2%A0embarked%20on%20a%20solo%20climb%20up%20the%20ladder.%20However%2C%20he%20slipped%20and%20fell%20into%20the%20valley%20below.%20Police%20officers%20and%20a%20pair%20of%20rescue%20helicopters%20rushed%20to%20the%20scene%20following%20