C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66867159.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Explains%3A%20How%20Soon%20Can%20Women's%20Quota%20Bill%20Come%20Into%20Effect%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fwomens-reservation-bill%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen's%20reservation%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0sailed%20through%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday%20-%20454%20MPs%20voted%20in%20favour%20and%20two%20against%20-%20after%20hours%20of%20ferocious%20attack-counterattack%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20will%20now%20be%20presented%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%2013%20years%20after%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20tabled%20its%20version%20of%20the%20proposed%20legislation%2C%20and%20it%20is%20widely%20expected%20to%20clear%20this%20second%20and%20hurdle%20too%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20confident%20of%20support%20from%20select%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20told%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20elections%20(next%20year)%2C%20soon%20census%20and%20delimitation%20exercise%20will%20take%20place.%20After%20this%2C%20there%20will%20be%201%2F3%20women%20in%20this%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20opposition%20MPs%20pointed%20out%2C%20the%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20legislatures%20will%20not%20actually%20become%20a%20reality%20after%20the%20bill%20becomes%20law%20because%20of%20provisions%20that%20require%20a%20census%20and%20a%20delimitation%20exercise%2C%20the%20first%20of%20which%20cannot%20take%20place%20before%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3ESo%2C%20When%20Can%20Women's%20Quota%20Bill%20Become%20Law%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20-%20almost%20certainly%20not%20before%20the%202029%20election%20-%20unless%20there%20is%20a%20seismic%20shift%20in%20the%20government's%20stance%20coupled%20with%20amendments%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20And%2C%20if%20political%20commentators%20like%20Swaraj%20India%20chief%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20are%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20it%20may%20not%20happen%20till%202039%2C%20over%2015%20years%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-details-of-what-womens-reservation-bill-says-4403339%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen's%20Quota%20Only%20By%202029%3F%20Exclusive%20Details%20Of%20New%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENDTV%20will%20attempt%20to%20work%20out%20a%20tentative%20timeline%2C%20and%20we%20begin%20with%20the%20Home%20Minister's%20rebuttal%20to%20opposition%20MPs'%20questions%20on%20the%20provisions%20about%20a%20census%20and%20delimitation%20(in%20that%20order).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Amit%20Shah%20Said%20On%20Census%2C%20Delimitation%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20shouted%20down%20the%20Opposition%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20declaring%20that%20a%20delimitation%20exercise%20was%20the%20only%20%26quot%3Btransparent%26quot%3B%20way%20to%20decide%20which%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha's%20543%20seat%20were%20to%20be%20reserved%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECensus%20data%2C%20he%20added%2C%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bbedrock%26quot%3B%20on%20which%20such%20decisions%20should%20be%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-about-politics-its-need-of-the-hour-amit-shah-on-womens-reservation-bill-4407612%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhy%20Delay%2C%20Delimitation%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20On%20Opposition's%20Big%20Women's%20Quota%20Query%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20delimitation%2C%20per%20Article%2082%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20is%20after%20the%20first%20census%20post-2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20census%20is%20scheduled%20for%202031%3B%20one%20was%20to%20take%20place%20in%202021%20but%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20prevented%20those%20plans%2C%20and%20that%20exercise%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20seemed%20to%20indicate%2C%20may%20now%20be%20held%20after%20the%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReports%20suggest%20this%20will%20not%20take%20place%20till%202025%2C%20meaning%20data%20collection%20and%20tabulation%20followed%20by%20release%20is%20not%20likely%20before%202027.%20Delimitation%20must%20then%20take%20place%20before%20the%20bill%20is%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20redrawing%20of%20constituency%20boundaries%20is%20an%20exhaustive%20process%20and%20this%20could%20take%20two-three%20years%2C%20meaning%20it%20may%20not%20be%20completed%20before%20the%202029%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EDelimitation%20Ahead%20Of%20Schedule%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20delimitation%20exercise%20can%20take%20place%20sooner%2C%20but%20that%20requires%20Article%2082%20to%20be%20amended.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20southern%20states%20-%20more%20successful%20in%20controlling%20their%20population%20-%20have%20voiced%20concerns%20over%20reduced%20representation%20following%20redrawing%20of%20constituencies%20based%20on%20population%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-explainer-what-is-womens-reservation-bill-4402338%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENDTV%20Explainer%3A%20What%20Is%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20they%20fear%20states%20that%20failed%20to%20control%20population%20will%20have%20more%20control%20over%20the%20government%20and%20greater%20influence%20in%20deciding%20policies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20get%20more%20funds%20from%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EWomen's%20Reservation%20In%202039%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20to%20caution%20against%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20media%20reports%2C%20highlighting%20%26quot%3Bthe%20real%20significance%20of%20the%20delimitation%20clause%26quot%3B%20and%20stating%20%26quot%3Bactually%2C%20it%20(implementation%20of%20the%20women's%20bill)%20may%20not%20happen%20till%202039%26quot%3B.%20This%20assumes%20no%20census%20activity%20till%20the%20next%20scheduled%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArticle%2082%20(amended%20in%202001)%20virtually%20bars%20delimitation%20prior%20to%20the%20first%20census%20figures%20post%202026.%20That%20can%20only%20be%202031.%20Most%20observers%20don't%20remember%20delimitation%20takes%20three%20to%20four%20years%20(last%20one%20took%20five)%20to%20give%20its%20final%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMedia%20reports%20say%20Women's%20reservation%20would%20happen%20in%202029.%20This%20is%20misleading.%20Actually%20it%20may%20not%20happen%20till%202039.%3Cbr%3E%20Most%20media%20reports%20miss%20the%20real%20significance%20of%20the%20delimitation%20clause.%3Cbr%3E%20Article%2082%20(amended%20in%202001)%20virtually%20bars%20delimitation%20prior%20to%20the%20first%20census%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20(%40_YogendraYadav)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F_YogendraYadav%2Fstatus%2F1704350382653354011%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBesides%2C%20the%20coming%20delimitation%20can%20be%20very%20contentious%20given%20the%20population%20ratio%20changes.%20So%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20a%20report%20around%202037%20or%20so...%20that%20can%20only%20be%20implemented%20in%202039.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Does%20The%20Woman's%20Bill%20Say%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20six-page%20bill%20says%20a%20third%20of%20seats%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20Assemblies%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20and%20filled%20by%20direct%20election