y%20systems%20and%20platforms%20is%20also%20being%20organised%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%2013th%20edition%20of%20the%20IPACC%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20is%20also%20hosting%20the%2047th%20Indo%20Pacific%20Armies%20Management%20Seminar%20(IPAMS)%20and%20the%20Senior%20Enlisted%20Leaders%20Forum%20(SELF).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVice%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20Lt%20Gen%20MV%20Suchindra%20Kumar%20said%20the%20event%20will%20provide%20a%20unique%20opportunity%20to%20build%20common%20perspectives%20towards%20a%20shared%20vision%20and%20that%20it%20will%20help%20strengthen%20friendships%20through%20the%20formidable%20and%20indelible%20%26quot%3Bsoldierly%20bond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IPACC%2C%20instituted%20as%20a%20biennial%20event%20in%201999%2C%20is%20attended%20by%20Army%20chiefs%20of%20countries%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20to%20discuss%20issues%20of%20mutual%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20current%20edition%20of%20this%20conclave%20is%20very%20special%2C%20as%20it%20will%20witness%20participation%20of%20full%20spectrum%20of%20military%20ranks%2C%20from%20Army%20chiefs%20to%20non-commissioned%20Officers%20from%2022%20nationalities%2C%20and%20their%20spouses%2C%26quot%3B%20Lt%20Gen%20Kumar%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFifteen%20Army%20chiefs%20and%20delegations%20from%2022%20countries%20will%20attend%20this%20event%20in%20Delhi.%20I%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20thank%20the%20US%20Army%2C%20especially%20US%20Army%20Pacific%2C%20who%20are%20our%20co-hosts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indo-Pacific%20Armies%20Management%20Seminar%20(IPAMS)%2C%20held%20annually%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20conferences%20for%20the%20land%20forces%20in%20the%20region%20which%20is%20organised%20annually%20by%20US%20Army%20Pacific%2C%20along%20with%20a%20co-host%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%2C%20the%20Vice%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff