cape%2C%20both%20economically%20and%20strategically%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Vice%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20deliberate%20on%20the%20multifaceted%20challenges%20and%20opportunities%20that%20lie%20ahead%2C%20we%20are%20reminded%20that%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20is%20not%20just%20a%20geographical%20expanse%2C%20but%20a%20stage%20where%20nations%20unite%20to%20shape%20the%20narrative%20of%20our%20shared%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695223920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fqdebj3g8_army-chief-manoj-pande-pti-650-_650x400_12_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-host-indo-pacific-army-chiefs-conclave-22-nations-to-attend-4406685%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Army%20will%20host%20a%20two-day%20conference%20of%20Army%20chiefs%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20nations%20next%20week%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20evolve%20a%20common%20strategy%20to%20ensure%20peace%2C%20prosperity%20and%20stability%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20growing%20global%20concerns%20over%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-host-indo-pacific-army-chiefs-conclave-22-nations-to-attend-4406685%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-host-indo-pacific-army-chiefs-conclave-22-nations-to-attend-4406685%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-host-indo-pacific-army-chiefs-conclave-22-nations-to-attend-4406685%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOnly%20Question%20Mark%20Would%20Have%20Been...%26quot%3B%3A%20Gavaskar%