-on-kl-rahuls-comeback-4401017%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fasia-cup-2023-only-question-mark-would-have-been-sunil-gavaskar-on-kl-rahuls-comeback-4401017%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women's%20Quota%20Bill%20Passes%20Lok%20Sabha%20Test%2C%20Step%20Closer%20To%20Being%20Law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20bill%20was%20passed%20through%20voice%20vote%20in%20new%20parliament%20during%20a%20five-day%20special%20session%20called%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%2075%20years%20of%20Indian%20Independence.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20bill%20was%20passed%20with%20the%20support%20of%20454%20MPs.%20Only%20Two%20MPs%20voted%20against%20it.%20The%20bill%20will%20be%20presented%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20tomorrow%2C%20Day%20Four%20of%20the%20special%20session.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20the%20quota%2C%20though%2C%20can%20take%20place%20only%20after%20a%20census%20and%20delimitation%2C%20which%20pushes%20it%20back%20by%20at%20least%20six%20years%20--%20a%20matter%20that%20has%20provided%20ammunition%20to%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20however%2C%20said%20both%20delimitation%20and%20census%20will%20begin%20after%20next%20year's%20general%20election.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20bill%20has%20been%20able%20to%20clear%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%202008%20bill%20drafted%20by%20the%20UPA%20government%20was%20only%20able%20to%20clear%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20test%20before%20being%20scuttled%20by%20parties%20demanding%20quota%20for%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20as%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EMr%20Shah%20yesterday%20accused%20Opposition%20parties%20of%20lacking%20the%20will%20to%20push%20through%20the%20bill%20and%20playing%20politics%20over%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20fifth%20attempt%20to%20bring%20this%20bill%20--%20From%20HD%20Devegowda%20to%20Manmohan%20Singh.%20What%20were%20the%20reasons%20why%20it%20failed%20to%20get%20nod%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20tracing%20the%20bill's%20journey%20each%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOpening%20the%20debate%2C%20Congress's%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20underscored%20that%20the%20initiative%20for%20the%20bill%20was%20taken%20under%20the%20UPA%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BHow%20many%20years%20will%20they%20(women)%20have%20to%20wait...%20two...%20four...%20eight%3F%20Is%20this%20right%3F%20Congress%20demands%20the%20bill%20be%20implemented%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20calling%20for%20reservation%20for%20women%20from%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20communities.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECongress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTwo%20things%20seem%20strange.%20One%2C%20the%20Idea%20that%20you%20need%20new%20census%20for%20this%20bill%20and%20new%20delimitation%20and%20I%20think%20this%20bill%20can%20be%20implemented%20today.%20I%20wonder%20this%20is%20not%20designed%20to%20push%20it%20forward%20by%20seven%20or%20eight%20years%20and%20let%20it%20play%20out%20the%20way%20it%20does%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695222240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fovml5cm8_new-parliament_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-passes-lok-sabha-test-step-closer-to-being-law-10-points-4408091%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20historic%20bill%20providing%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20assemblies%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday%20after%20hours%20of%20fierce%20debate.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20bill%20was%20introduced%20and%20passed%20in%20the%20lower%20house.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-passes-lok-sabha-test-step-closer-to-being-law-10-points-4408091%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-n