0about%20the%20fact%20that%20Hyderabad%20was%20chosen%20as%20an%20off-site%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fgandhis-steal-the-show-at-congress-working-committee-meeting-in-hyderabad%2Farticle67315850.ece%5C%22%3Edestination%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%20meeting%20to%20send%20a%20message%20to%20the%20electorate%20of%20the%20poll-bound%20Telangana%2C%20where%20the%20party%20is%20eyeing%20a%20shot%20at%20power.%20The%20spokespersons%20also%20said%20that%20the%20CWC%20will%20actively%20engage%20with%20issues%20concerning%20the%20state%20units%20of%20poll-bound%20states%2C%20while%20its%20senior%20leaders%20spoke%20about%20the%20need%20for%20rival%20leaders%20within%20the%20party%20to%20stop%20speaking%20against%20each%20other%20in%20front%20of%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20also%20highlighted%20that%20the%20election%20of%20the%20party%20president%20in%20the%20Congress%20is%20unique%20and%20reflects%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20functioning%2C%20contrasting%20it%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20one-way%20high%20command.%20All%20of%20this%20comes%20along%20with%20a%20continuing%20organisational%20overhaul%20of%20the%20guidelines%20decided%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-chintan-shivir-udaipur-bharat-jodo%5C%22%3EChintan%20Shivir%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20party%20spokespersons%2C%20Pawan%20Khera%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20CWC%20meeting%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20last%20year%2C%20you%20have%20seen%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20has%20been%20literally%20on%20the%20roads%20of%20this%20country%2C%20picking%20up%20issues%20of%20the%20people%2C%20addressing%20the%20issues%20of%20the%20people%2C%20talking%20about%20issues%2C%20which%20unfortunately%20do%20not%20find%20to%20be%20in%20the%20mainstream%20of%20our%20narrative%20anymore%20for%20the%20last%20nine%20years%E2%80%A6A%20lot%20of%20you%20had%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Congress%20party%20that%20we%20are%20not%20there%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20this%20country.%20I%20hope%20that%20complaint%20is%20over%20now.%20Shri%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20undertook%20the%20hardest%204%2C000-kilometre%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20continues%20even%20now%2C%20as%20we%20speak%2C%20because%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20way%20we%20do%20our%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20political%20and%20organisational%20messaging%20has%20been%20direct%20and%20to%20the%20point%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20unusual%20in%20the%20grand%20old%20party.%20The%20party%20appears%20alive%20and%20kicking%2C%20and%20seems%20to%20have%20left%20behind%20its%20laggard%20workings%20after%202014.%20How%20much%20this%20newfound%20energy%20will%20help%20the%20Congress%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20but%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20has%20truly%20proven%20to%20be%2C%20as%20Khera%20said%2C%20a%20turning%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695221985000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20202024%2FScreenshot-2023-09-20-at-8.19.40-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsonia-gandhi-womens-reservation-debate-congress-renewed-energy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20party%20appears%20alive%20and%20kicking%2C%20and%20seems%20to%20have%20left%20behind%20its%20laggard%20workings%20after%202014.%20The%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20may%20have%20truly%20proven%20to%20be%20the%20turning%20point.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsonia-gandhi-womens-reservation-debate-congress-renewed-energy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Voting%20On%20Women's%20Quota%20In%20New%20Parliament%20Took%20Time%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVoting%20on%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20today%20took%20time%20due%20to%20several%20reasons%2C%20one%20of%20them%20being%20the%20absence%20of%20electronic%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20women's%20quota%20bill%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20after%20a%20long%20debate%20between%20ruling%20party%20leaders%20and%20the%20Opposition.%20It%20proposes%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20voting%20took%20time%20as%20the%20leaders%20were%20not%20yet%20assigned%20seats%20and%20divisions%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%2C%20which%20prevented%20electronic%20voting%20from%20taking%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20other%20complaints%20of%20not%20getting%20proper%20audio%20connections%20and%20members%20upset%20with%20the%20new%20bills%20suddenly%20popping%20on%20their%20screen.%20This%20prompted%20the%20Speaker%20to%20concede%2C%20who%20said%20there%20could%20be%20such%20issues%20initially%20in%20the%20new%20house%2C%20and%20they%20will%20sort%20them%20out%20in%20no%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20held%20sessions%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20old%20parliament%20has%20been%20named%20Samvidhan%20Sadan%20(Constitution%20House).%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20The%20Constitution%20Hall%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20has%20a%20digitised%20copy%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20along%20with%20a%20touch%20of%20modernity%20as%20it%20also%20houses%20a%20Foucault's%20pendulum%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20rotation%20of%20the%20Earth.%20The%20Foucault's%20Pendulum%20hangs%20from%20a%20large%20skylight%20from%20the%20triangular%20roof%20of%20the%20Constitution%20Hall%20and%20signifies%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20with%20that%20of%20the%20universe.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chambers%20have%20digitised%20voting%20systems%2C%20well-engineered%20acoustics%2C%20and%20state-of-the-art%20audio%20and%20visual%20systems%20to%20ensure%20effective%20legislative%20proceedings.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20Twenty-seven%20women%20MPs%20cutting%20across%20party%20lines%20spoke%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20today%2C%20with%20BJP%20MPs%20coming%20out%20in%20support%20of%20it%20and%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20also%20backing%20it%20while%20demanding%20its%20immediate%20implementation.%20At%20present%2C%20there%20are%2082%20women%20MPs%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20out%20of%20the%20total%20strength%20of%20543.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695221940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fe7uafvb_old-and-new-parliament_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-voting-on-womens-quota-in-new-parliament-took-time-today-4408178%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Voting%20on%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20today%20took%20time%20due%20to%20several%20reasons%2C%20one%20of%20them%20being%20the%20absence%20of%20electronic%20voting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-voting-on-womens-quota-in-new-parliament-took-time-today-4408178%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-voting-on-womens-quota-in-new-parliament-took-time-today-4408178%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-voting-on-womens-quota-in-new-parliament-took-time-today-4408178%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%3A%20Hackers%20claim%20ex-president%20dead%20on%20son's%20X%20account%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695221665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbrande