minant%20religion%20in%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Lutfiawati%C2%A0was%20found%20guilty%20of%20%26quot%3Bspreading%20information%20aimed%20at%20inciting%20hatred%20against%20religious%20individuals%20and%20specific%20groups%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20court%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20the%20South%20Sumatra%20city%20of%20Palembang%2C%20according%20to%20the%20verdict.%20She%20has%20also%20been%20ordered%20to%20pay%20a%20fine%20of%20%2416%2C245%20(Rs%C2%A013%2C48%2C111).%20If%20she%20fails%20to%20pay%20the%20money%2C%20her%20jail%C2%A0term%20may%20be%20extended%20by%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETaken%20aback%20by%20the%20verdict%2C%20she%20told%20a%C2%A0local%20news%20station%20that%20she%20knew%20that%20she%20made%20a%20mistake%2C%20but%20''did%20not%20expect%20such%20a%20severe%20punishment.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Ms%20Lutfiawati%20loves%C2%A0Bollywood%20movies%20and%20has%20also%20adopted%20the%C2%A0Indian%20name%20Lina%20Mukherjee.%20The%20influencer%2C%20who%20has%20more%20than%20two%20million%20TikTok%20followers%2C%20also%20runs%20a%20business%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20case%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20high-profile%20blasphemy%20convictions%20in%20recent%20years.%20Last%20year%2C%C2%A0six%20people%20were%20arrested%20after%20a%20bar%20chain%20promoted%20free%20alcohol%20for%20patrons%20named%20Mohammed%2C%20as%20per%20an%20AFP%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUsman%20Hamid%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20Amnesty%20International%20Indonesia%2C%20said%20the%20blasphemy%20article%20in%20Indonesian%20law%20has%20been%20abused%20to%20target%20minority%20groups%20and%20dissenters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695221220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F7j0c9d8g_tiktok-generic-reuters_625x300_04_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n