0election%20approaches%2C%20the%20government%20puts%20up%20an%20anti-inflation%20fa%C3%A7ade%20and%20reduces%20the%20prices%20of%20commodities%20which%20it%20increased%20earlier.%20The%20recent%20reduction%20of%20domestic%20LPG%20prices%20by%20Rs%20200%20is%20an%20example.%20While%20the%20reduction%20is%20a%20drop%20in%20the%20ocean%2C%20it%20does%20provide%20some%20relief%20to%20lakhs%20of%20struggling%20families%20and%20should%20be%20welcomed.%20Persistently%20high%20inflation%20has%20been%20a%20constant%20alongside%20high%20unemployment%20and%20tepid%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20consumer%20price%20inflation%20was%20at%206.83%25.%20In%20the%20last%2029%20months%2C%20inflation%20has%20been%20above%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20target%20level%20of%204%25%3B%20on%2016%20occasions%2C%20it%20crossed%20the%20%E2%80%98tolerance%20level%E2%80%99%20of%206%25.%20Food%20inflation%20has%20been%20unsustainably%20high%2C%20crossing%2010%25%20and%209%25%20in%20July%20and%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20of%20consumer%20prices%20and%20employment%20data%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F15d5ceac-c10b-4911-a6a5-38ab782bd4bd%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F15d5ceac-c10b-4911-a6a5-38ab782bd4bd%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1695286050762000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3DbP53y0wpD8U0pxGL4D3o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20preparing%20meals%20has%20risen%2065%25%20in%20five%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20wages%20rose%20only%2028-37%25.%20The%20price%20rise%20is%20squeezing%20household%20budgets%2C%20leaving%20less%20room%20for%20other%20essential%20expenditures.%20This%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20the%20demand%20slump%20in%20the%20larger%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20food%20inflation%2C%20the%20government%20hurriedly%20points%20towards%20rising%20inflation%20in%20developing%20countries%20%E2%80%95%20%E2%80%9Ceverybody%20is%20suffering%E2%80%9D.%20This%20is%20facetious%20reasoning%20and%20deserves%20to%20be%20summarily%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fwill-voters-wait-hungrily-for-amrit-kaal-or-will-food-inflation-decide-the-elections%5C%22%3EWill%20Voters%20Wait%20Hungrily%20for%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20Will%20Food%20Inflation%20Decide%20the%20Elections%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20majority%20in%20high%20income%20countries%2C%20inflation%20impacts%20discretionary%20expenditure.%20In%20lower%20middle%20income%20countries%20like%20ours%2C%20inflation%20has%20a%20direct%20and%20often%20painful%20bearing%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20life.%20High%20inflation%20in%20Europe%20may%20lead%20to%20families%20deferring%20a%20car%20purchase%20or%20a%20holiday.%20In%20India%2C%20it%20leads%20to%20a%20reduction%20in%20food%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWeeks%20ago%2C%20when%20tomato%20prices%20crossed%20Rs%20100%2Fkilogram%2C%20most%20households%20drastically%20cut%20consumption.%20A%20survey%20from%20early%202023%20shows%20that%20rising%20milk%20prices%20led%20to%2040%25%20of%20families%20either%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F8eb9a977-46ba-4878-bd15-951ab3d92bd7%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F8eb9a977-46ba-4878-bd15-951ab3d92bd7%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1695286050762000%26amp%3Bu