%20justify%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20which%20has%20lately%20faced%20public%20backlash%20in%20Jammu%2C%20also%20took%20a%20cautious%20stance%20on%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20saying%20that%20not%20having%20an%20elected%20government%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20the%20option.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESinha%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20came%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20set%20out%20a%20timeframe%20for%20holding%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20during%20the%20hearing%20of%20Article%20370%20petitions%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20function%20recently%2C%20Sinha%20claimed%20that%20if%20an%20%E2%80%9Cindependent%20and%20secret%E2%80%9D%20survey%20was%20conducted%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20%E2%80%9C80%25%20of%20people%20will%20vote%20that%20the%20present%20system%20should%20continue%20and%20no%20other%20system%20is%20required.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20telling%20you%20the%20opinion%20of%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sinha%20claimed%2C%20without%20citing%20any%20evidence.%20Assembly%20elections%20have%20been%20due%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20since%202018%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20coalition%20government%20headed%20by%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20president%20Mehbooba%20Mufti.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20some%20people%20who%20are%20in%20pain.%20For%20them%2C%20it%20is%20a%20problem.%20They%20can%20say%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued%2C%20pointing%20obliquely%20to%20the%20Kashmir-based%20political%20parties%20who%20have%20also%20been%20urging%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20to%20hold%20the%20polls%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Arun%20Gupta%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20BJP%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20that%20the%20party%20was%20prepared%20for%20assembly%20elections.%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20he%20(Sinha)%20has%20said%2C%20it%20is%20his%20opinion.%20As%20far%20as%20the%20BJP%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20for%20elections%20as%20a%20political%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20BJP%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%2C%20Ashok%20Koul%2C%20said%20that%20the%20ECI%20will%20take%20the%20final%20call%20for%20holding%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20the%20ECI%20comes%20out%20with%20the%20poll%20schedule%2C%20I%20am%20sure%20all%20the%20parties%20will%20be%20ready%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPressed%20about%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20Koul%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CHe%20(Sinha)%20also%20believes%20in%20democracy.%20We%20cannot%20say%20no%20to%20elected%20representatives.%20No%20one%20can%20reject%20(the%20importance%20of)%20elected%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Koul%20has%20also%20advocated%20for%20conducting%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20wariness%20in%20reacting%20to%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20pressure%20that%20the%20party%20is%20facing%20in%20Jammu%2C%20the%20Hindu-majority%20region%20of%20the%20UT%20and%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20stronghold%2C%20where%20a%20shutdown%20was%20recently%20observed%20against%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20toll%20plaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20parties%20slam%20LG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20Naeem%20Akhtar%2C%20senior%20PDP%20leader%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20he%20claimed%20100%25%20of%20people%20favour%20central%20rule%2C%20how%20could%20one%20test%20its%20veracity%3F%20All%20the%20accepted%20methods%20of%20gauging%20public%20opinion%20are%20frozen%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20sarcastically%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20for%20one%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20anything%20offensive%20in%20what%20LG%20(Sinha)%20says.%20One%20just%20has%20to%20realise%20the%20spirit%20of%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98New%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99%20where%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20matter%20for%20anything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20Progressive%20Azad%20Party%20(DAP)%20%E2%80%93%20led%20by%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20%E2%80%93%20termed%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20as%20%E2%80%9Chighly%20unacceptable%20and%20irresponsible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20the%20temple%20of%20democracy%20where%20only%20the%20elected%20government%20can%20speak%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20people.%20The%20statement%20(of%20Sinha)%20is%20not%20just%20challenging%20the%20democratic%20ethos%20that%20India%20is%20globally%20known%20for%20but%20equally%20a%20dangerous%20trend%20that%20we%20all%20shall%20oppose%20tooth%20and%20nail%2C%E2%80%9D%20DAP%20spokesperson%20Salman%20Nizami%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20craving%20for%20democratic%20rule%2C%20which%20has%20been%20denied%20to%20us%20for%20almost%20six%20years.%20Let%20the%20elections%20be%20held%20and%20LG%20saheb%20will%20get%20a%20reply%20from%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeet%20the%20new%20king%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20who%20is%20so%20desperate%20to%20remain%20the%20uncrowned%20ruler%20that%20he%20now%20invents%20surveys%20to%20justify%20his%20unwillingness%20to%20conduct%20assembly%20elections.%20India%20is%20truly%20the%20%E2%80%98mother%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99%20%26amp%3B%20we%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20her%20orphan%20children.%20Perhaps%20this%20is%20the%20logic%20BJP%20will%20start%20using%20to%20stop%20having%20elections%20nationwide%20%E2%80%93%20One%20Nation%2C%20No%20Election.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20