280%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FSheikh_Hasina1.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FSheikh_Hasina1-300x159.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FSheikh_Hasina1-1024x543.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-3188%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22679%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESheikh%20Hasina%2C%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20Awami%20League.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20participating%20in%20any%20kind%20of%20polls%20that%20are%20not%20inclusive%20or%20boycotted%20by%20most%20of%20the%20major%20political%20parties%20can%20even%20lead%20to%20the%20split%20of%20Jamaat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20Jamaat%20has%20become%20a%20relic%20of%20the%20Cold%20War.%20The%20party%2C%20a%20group%20similar%20to%20Muslim%20brotherhood%2C%20has%20been%20crucial%20for%20the%20US%20in%20the%20early%20and%20late%201970s%20as%20its%20role%20was%20pivotal%20in%20fighting%20the%20Left%20in%20the%20Muslim%20majority%20Bangladesh%20and%20Pakistan.%20During%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98war%20on%20terror%E2%80%99%2C%20Jamaat%20kept%20a%20centrist%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20interest%20is%20more%20centred%20around%20containing%20China%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20the%20party%20will%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20make%20itself%20look%20useful.%20Also%20troubling%20for%20Jamaat%20is%20its%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20apparent%20inability%20to%20find%20its%20role%20in%20this%20changed%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProblematic%2C%20too%2C%20is%20its%20Leninist%20party%20structure%2C%20which%20is%20good%20for%20a%20revolutionary%20party.%20But%20Jamaat%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20big%20mass%20organisation%20from%20which%20it%20can%20draw%20new%20members.%20This%20lack%20of%20inclusiveness%20has%20made%20th