ead%20of%20the%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%20(RAW)%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20was%20immediately%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20international%20media%20and%20generated%20quite%20a%20ripple%20across%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTVietor08%2Fstatus%2F1703862306613117111%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20big%20because%20the%20Canadians%20have%20accused%20the%20Indian%20government%20%E2%80%93%20not%20any%20private%20vigilante%20group%20or%20organisation%20%E2%80%93%20of%20murder%20in%20a%20foreign%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20and%20Canadian%20state%20services%20seem%20to%20have%20taken%20this%20as%20seriously%20as%20the%20UK%20did%20when%20the%20Russian%20%C3%A9migr%C3%A9%20Alexander%20Litvinenko%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2021%2F09%2F21%2F1039224996%2Frussia-alexander-litvinenko-european-court-human-rights-putin%5C%22%3Ewas%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allegedly%20on%20orders%20of%20the%20Kremlin.%20It%20is%20extraordinarily%20rare%20for%20a%20Western%20democracy%20to%20expel%20a%20diplomat%20from%20another%20democracy%20on%20these%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%201st%20time%20a%20foreign%20govt%2C%20barring%20Pakistan%2C%20has%20accused%20Delhi%20of%20an%20act%20of%20violence%20on%20their%20soil.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20allegations%20that%20Indian%20forces%2Fagents%20acted%20abroad%20in%20contravention%20of%20intl%20law%20were%20made%20recently%20in%20two%20high%20profile%20cases.%201%2F2%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsY5VfbPrX0%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsY5VfbPrX0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Siddharth%20(%40svaradarajan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsvaradarajan%2Fstatus%2F1704037410269458905%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20this%20ought%20to%20be%20a%20major%20embarrassment%20for%20Modi.%20Western%20media%20headlines%20will%20not%20be%20flattering%20for%20a%20few%20days%20but%20he%20is%20bound%20to%20weather%20this.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20altercation%20with%20Canada%20is%20likely%20to%20serve%20him%20politically%20well%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20Nijjar%2C%20the%20Sikh%20leader%20who%20was%20killed%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobalnews.ca%2Fnews%2F9969537%2Fwho-is-hardeep-singh-nijjar%2F%5C%22%3Eterrorist%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20India.%20New%20Delhi%20claims%20that%20he%20was%20the%20mastermind%20of%20the%20separatist%20militant%20group%2C%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force.%20Nijjar%20was%20an%20accused%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-khalistan-speculation%5C%22%3Eseveral%20terrorist%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20named%20in%20an%20Interpol%20notice%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ckey%20conspirator%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%202007%20bombing%20of%20a%20cinema%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20gains%20from%20this%20because%20his%20base%20has%20a%20tendency%20to%20celebrate%20aggressive%20initiatives%20against%20adversaries.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20fans%20were%20jubilant%20when%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20conducted%20airstrikes%20in%20the%20Pakistani%20territory%20after%20the%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20Pulwama%20in%202019.%20The%20alleged%20act%20of%20organising%20a%20terrorist%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20in%20a%20foreign%20land%20would%20seem%20quite%20redolent%20of%20Mossad%E2%80%99s%20ways%2C%20which%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20fans%20adore.%20Expect%20Modi%20to%20be%20hailed%2C%20those%20involved%20to%20become%20heroes%2C%20and%20perhaps%20a%20movie%20script%20may%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20media%20will%20explain%20this%20away%20as%20Trudeau%20pandering%20to%20the%20Sikh%20vote%20in%20Canada.%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20move%20may%20not%20be%20bereft%20of%20political%20calculation%3B%20he%20may%20also%20be%20caught%20between%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20Canadian%20law%20enforcement%20%E2%80%93%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20act%20on%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20official%20need%20to%20maintain%20ties%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20point%20of%20view%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20did%20transgress%20established%20norms%20between%20political%20elites.%20There%20are%20processes%20about%20dealing%20with%20terrorists%20residing%20in%20other%20countries.%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20view%20would%20be%20that%20you%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20out%20people%20if%20those%20processes%20do%20not%20work%20for%20you.%20There%20are%20rules%20to%20follow%20and%20colleagues%20in%20the%20governing%20class%20do%20not%20create%20domestic%20political%20situations%20and%20problems%20for%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20said%20this%20controversy%20should%20make%20no%20difference%20to%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20public%20affirmation%20of%20Modi%2C%20however%20indignant%20they%20may%20be%20in%20private.%20Its%20leaders%20have%20been%20perfectly%20happy%20to%20deal%20with%20him%20and%20consume%20his%20platitudes%20about%20democracy%2C%20so%20long%20as%20he%20buys%20their%20weapons%20and%20provides%20market%20access.%20And%20this%20is%20reflected%20in%20their%20reaction%20to%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20move.%20The%20US%20and%20Australia%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20concern%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20allegation%2C%20while%20the%20UK%20Foreign%20Secretary%20James%20Cleverly%20did%20not%20name%20India%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJamesCleverly%2Fstatus%2F1704160204739272930%5C%22%3Etweet%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAll%20countries%20should%20respect%20sovereignty%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20in%20regular%20contact%20with%20our%20Canadian%20partners%20about%20serious%20allegations%20raised%20in%20the%20Canadian%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImportant%20that%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20runs%20its%20course%20and%20the%20perpetrators%20brought%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20James%20Cleverly%F0%9F%87%AC%F0%9F%87%A7%20(%40JamesCleverly)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJamesCleverly%2Fstatus%2F1704160204739272930%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ci%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F09%2F19%2Findia-expels-canada-diplomat-sikh-assassination%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20allies%20refused%20to%20join%20Ottawa%20in%20publicly%20condemning%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EUnwanted%20attention%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20controversy%20will%20not%20be%20without%20its%20costs%20and%20consequences%20for%20Indian%20immigrants%20more%20broadly.%20Around%2018%20million%20Indians%20currently%20live%20abroad%3B%20over%20210%2C000%20of%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fcanada-aims-300-000-immigrants-by-mar-2023-how-will-indians-benefit-11666324812953.html%5C%22%3Etook%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fstuartanderson%2F2023%2F03%2F06%2Findian-immigration-to-canada-has-tripled-since-2013%2F%3Fsh%3D2f282a915620%5C%22%3Epermanent%20residency%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Canada%20in%202021%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20kind%20of%20a%20story%20brings%20unwanted%20attention%20on%20Indians%20living%20abroad%20%E2%80%93%20as%20any%20scrutiny%20into%20the%20activities%20of%20a%20foreign%20government%20on%20home%20soil%20is%20bound%20to%20bring%20along%20a%20measure%20of%20focus%20on%20the%20diaspora%2C%20as%20Chinese%20nationals%20living%20in%20Western%20countries%20know%20very%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20noted%20in%20his%20statement%20that%20his%20country%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20working%20closely%20and%20coordinating%20with%20%5Bits%5D%20allies%20on%20this%20very%20serious%20matter.%E2%80%9D%20Canada%20is%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20intelligence%20sharing%20agreement%20along%20with%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20is%20not%20inconceivable%20that%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20in%20these%20countries%20will%20be%20together%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20organised%20diaspora%20activity%20and%20its%20links%20to%20Indian%20parties%20and%20government%20in%20the%20light%20of%20dramatic%20developments%20like%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWestern%20governments%20will%20not%20be%20oblivious%20to%20the%20growing%20right-wing%20activism%20among%20the%20diaspora%20and%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20harness%20that%20energy%20for%20political%20support%20and%20to%20stave%20off%20criticism%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20can%20arguably%20live%20with%20a%20measure%20of%20diaspora%20mobilization%20but%20not%20entirely%20look%20away%20when%20it%20is%20disrupting%20civil%20peace%20and%20the%20social%20climate%20in%20their%20own%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%2C%20to%20be%20sure%2C%20several%20unsavoury%20incidents%20in%20recent%20times%20involving%20Indian-origin%20immigrants.%20There%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F09%2F25%2Fnyregion%2Fbulldozer-indian-parade-new-jersey.html%5C%22%3Ebulldozers%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20parade%20in%20New%20Jersey%20that%20symbolically%20supported%20the%20demolition%20of%20Muslim%20homes%20in%20India%20by%20the%20BJP%20government.%20There%20were%20violent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fviolent-clashes-in-leicester-last-year-stoked-by-modis-hindu-nationalist-party-daily-mail%5C%22%3Ecommunal%20clashes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Leicester%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20last%20year.%20There%20were%20Sikh-Hindu%20clashes%20in%20Sydney%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2023-06-10%2Ftensions-over-khalistan-separatist-movement-boil-over-in-sydney%2F102463024%5C%22%3Ethis%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20reports%20have%20emerged%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Foz-police-see-hindu-hand-in-temple-graffiti-advise-closure%2Farticleshow%2F103744961.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Efindings%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20police%20in%20Queensland%20about%20the%20defacement%20of%20Hindu%20temples%20in%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EForeign%20governments%20will%20be%20keen%20to%20assess%20if%20such%20incidents%20develop%20organically%20or%20were%20provoked%20by%20foreign%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIntensified%20Sikh-Hindu%20schism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%E2%80%99s%20statement%20is%20likely%20to%20intensify%20the%20divide%20among%20various%20Indian-origin%20diaspora%20groups.%20Sikh%20and%20other%20minority%20groups%20will%20organise%20against%20Hindu%20nationalist%20organisations%20and%20pressure%20foreign%20governments%20to%20act%20against%20them%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Hindu%20Right%20will%20counter-mobilise%20and%20lobby.%20All%20concerned%20will%20be%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20Western%20bureaucratic%20interest%20and%20regulation.%20If%20Indians%20were%20to%20bring%20their%20domestic%20politics%20and%20divisions%20into%20other%20countries%2C%20it%20is%20only%20natural%20that%20governments%20of%20those%20lands%20would%20be%20more%20engaged%20in%20their%20surveillance%20of%20diaspora%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20middle%20class%20can%20scarcely%20afford%20to%20be%20drawn%20into%20unhelpful%20transnational%20political%20projects%2C%20especially%20when%20just%20about%20every%20Western%20country%20is%20seeing%20anti-immigrant%20opinion%20on%20the%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndians%20are%20largely%20known%20abroad%20for%20quietly%20getting%20on%20with%20their%20migrant%20lives.%20Importing%20illiberal%20norms%20and%20methods%20and%20reshaping%20the%20political%20cultures%20of%20host%20countries%20in%20undesirable%20ways%20is%20bound%20to%20provoke%20anti-immigrant%20sentiment%20that%20Indians%20have%20managed%20to%20avoid%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESushil%20Aaron%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20policy%20analyst.%20He%20tweets%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSushilAaron%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%40SushilAaron%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695209778000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F28151247%2FTrudeau1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanadas-allegations-will-bring-unwanted-attention-on-indian-immigrants-abroad%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Western%20governments%20will%20not%20be%20oblivious%20to%20the%20growing%20right-wing%20activism%20among%20the%20diaspora%20and%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20harness%20that%20energy%20for%20political%20support%20and%20to%20stave%20off%20criticism%20of%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanadas-allegations-will-bring-unwanted-attention-on-indian-immigrants-abroad%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akasa%20Air%20moves%20court%20for%20action%20against%20pilots%20not%20serving%20notice%20period%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695209453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-10%2F15%2Ffull%2F1665827637-6325.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fakasa-air-moves-court-for-action-against-pilots-not-serving-notice-period-123092000742_1.html%22%2C%22summary%2