%20link%20of%20Indian%20government%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20is%20described%20as%20a%20Khalistan%20terrorist%20by%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada%20had%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat%2C%20following%20which%20India%20also%20asked%20a%20Canadian%20high%20commission%20official%20to%20leave%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%8BIn%20view%20of%20growing%20anti-India%20activities%20and%20politically-condoned%20hate%20crimes%20and%20criminal%20violence%20in%20Canada%2C%20all%20Indian%20nationals%20there%20and%20those%20contemplating%20travel%20are%20urged%20to%20exercise%20utmost%20caution%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20MEA%20advisory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20threats%20have%20%E2%80%9Ctargeted%20Indian%20diplomats%20and%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20who%20oppose%20the%20anti-India%20agenda%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20nationals%20are%20therefore%20advised%20to%20avoid%20travelling%20to%20regions%20and%20potential%20venues%20in%20Canada%20that%20have%20seen%20such%20incidents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20specific%20demography%2C%20the%20advisory%20also%20asked%20Indian%20students%20%E2%80%9Cin%20particular%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexercise%20extreme%20caution%20and%20remain%20vigilant%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdeteriorating%20security%20environment%20in%20Canada%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20called%20on%20Indian%20nationals%20and%20students%20to%20register%20with%20the%20appropriate%20diplomatic%20missions%20or%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmadad.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3Emadad%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20portal.%20%E2%80%9CRegistration%20would%20enable%20the%20High%20Commission%20and%20the%20Consulates%20General%20to%20better%20connect%20with%20Indian%20citizens%20in%20Canada%20in%20the%20event%20of%20any%20emergency%20or%20untoward%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20that%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20some%20news%20portals%20and%20channels%2C%20including%20ANI%20and%20Times%20Now%2C%20had%20misreported%20that%20Canada%20had%20issued%20a%20new%20advisory%20against%20travel%20to%20India.%20However%2C%20as%20Alt%20News%20co-founder%20Mohammed%20Zubair%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzoo_bear%2Fstatus%2F1704346980183630070%5C%22%3Epointed%20out%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Canada%20has%20been%20issuing%20much%20the%20same%20advisory%20on%20India%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20and%20the%20developments%20of%20the%20last%20few%20days%20have%20not%20changed%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20advisory%20applies%20to%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20but%20Canada%20is%20home%20to%20a%20large%20Indian%20diaspora.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FInternational%2FwireStory%2Fcanadas-relationship-india-numbers-103323481%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCanada%2520is%2520home%2520to%2520nearly%2CApril%2520as%2520Sikh%2520Heritage%2520Month.%5C%22%3Elast%20census%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Canada%20in%202021%2C%20people%20of%20Indian%20origin%20account%20for%20around%203.7%25%20of%20the%20population.%20Sikh-Canadians%20are%20about%202%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20around%20800%2C000%20international%20students%20in%20Canada%2C%20out%20of%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FInternational%2FwireStory%2Fcanadas-relationship-india-numbers-103323481%5C%22%3E40%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20from%20India%2C%20as%20per%20Immigration%2C%20Refugees%20and%20Citizenship%20Canada%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fstuartanderson%2F2023%2F03%2F06%2Findian-immigration-to-canada-has-tripled-since-2013%2F%3Fsh%3D38186c015620%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20a%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20in%20March%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Indians%20immigrating%20to%20Canada%20has%20tripled%20since%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20reported%2C%20as%20per%20Canadian%20government%20datasets%2C%20that%20Indian%20immigration%20ranged%20between%2027%2C000%20and%2036%2C000%20per%20year%20between%202004%20and%202012.%20But%20the%20number%20of%20Indians%20who%20became%20permanent%20residents%20in%20Canada%20rose%20from%2032%2C828%20in%20Canada%20to%20118%2C095%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20India%20was%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20in%20number%20of%20legal%20immigrants%20to%20Canada%2C%20with%20China%20at%20a%20distant%20second%20at%2031%2C815%20persons%20and%20Afghanistan%20at%2023%2C735%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695205485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20155343%2FF5rfg46XkAAW0jL.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fexercise-utmost-caution-india-issues-advisory-for-those-considering-travel-to-canada%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20advisory%20said%20that%20threats%20have%20%E2%80%9Ctargeted%20Indian%20diplomats%20and%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20who%20oppose%20the%20anti-India%20agenda%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fexercise-utmost-caution-india-issues-advisory-for-those-considering-travel-to-canada%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Illegal'%3A%20Lawyers%20Slam%20Hyderabad%20Cops%20For%20Frisking%20People%20at%20Cafes%20as%20'Preventative%20Measure'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20152945%2Fsantosh.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20violation%20of%20privacy%2C%20the%20Santosh%20Nagar%20police%20in%20Hyderabad%20carried%20out%20a%20blanket%20search%20operation%20on%20September%2016%2C%20frisking%20over%20200%20customers%20in%20eateries%20under%20its%20jurisdiction.%20Police%20personnel%20frisked%20customers%20who%20were%20having%20their%20dinner%20and%20evening%20tea%2C%20and%20went%20through%20their%20pockets%20and%20wallets%2C%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpreventive%20measure.%E2%80%9D%20A%20video%20of%20this%20exercise%20shows%20the%20Station%20House%20Officer%20(SHO)%20entering%20a%20food%20outlet%20and%20asking%20the%20seated%20customers%20to%20stand%20up.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20remain%20standing%2C%20you%20will%20be%20frisked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20them%20and%20proceeds%20to%20direct%20his%20subordinates%20to%20frisk%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20did%20not%20yield%20any%20results.%20Nobody%20was%20found%20with%20any%20drugs%20nor%20were%20any%20weapons%20seized.%20Santosh%20Nagar%20SHO%20P.%20Shiva%20Chandra%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20they%20frisked%20the%20customers%20on%20suspicion%20of%20ganja%20(narcotic%20substance)%20or%20weapons%20possession.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20carried%20out%20searches%20in%2010%20eateries%20in%20our%20jurisdiction.%20We%20did%20not%20find%20anything%20in%20the%20search%2C%20but%20this%20is%20a%20preventive%20measure%20to%20stop%20any%20crime%20from%20occuring%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20lawyers%20argue%20that%20this%20arbitrary%20police%20action%20is%20illegal.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20atrocious%20to%20frisk%20citizens%20and%20go%20through%20their%20things.%20If%20the%20police%20suspect%20anyone%20of%20possessing%20any%20narcotic%20substance%2C%20they%20should%20be%20accompanied%20by%20a%20gazetted%20officer%20while%20carrying%20out%20the%20search.%20And%20before%20the%20search%20begins%2C%20the%20gazetted%20officer%20should%20thoroughly%20check%20the%20police%20personnel%20so%20that%20they%20do%20not%20plant%20any%20incriminating%20material%20on%20any%20suspect%20and%20frame%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20lawyer%20and%20president%20of%20Human%20Rights%20Forum%20(HRF)%2C%20G.%20Madhava%20Rao.%20HRF%20is%20a%20civil%20rights%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCarrying%20out%20such%20a%20search%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20gazetted%20officer%20is%20illegal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESearches%20carried%20out%20in%20poor%20localities%20has%20also%20raised%20concerns%20of%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20inherent%20bias%20against%20certain%20communities.%20For%20instance%2C%20Santosh%20Nagar%20is%20a%20Muslim-dominated%20area.%20And%20the%20police%20admit%20to%20profiling%20suspects%20based%20on%20their%20looks%2C%20attire%2C%20and%20vehicle.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20we%20are%20carrying%20out%20such%20a%20task.%20In%20our%20jurisdiction%2C%20we%20have%20a%20problem%20of%20ganja%20possession%20and%20other%20criminal%20activities.%20During%20vehicle%20checks%2C%20we%20regularly%20frisk%20suspects%20to%20search%20for%20ganja.%20We%20do%20fingerprint%20scanning%20and%20facial%20recognition%20of%20these%20suspects%20to%20check%20if%20they%20have%20any%20criminal%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SHO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20form%20of%20policing%20was%20previously%20slammed%20by%20many%20civil%20rights%20activists.%20In%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Fhyderabad-cops-are-illegally-checking-phones-whatsapp-citizens-part-drug-crackdown-156997%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2021%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%20the%20Hyderabad%20police%20faced%20severe%20backlash%20when%20they%20started%20checking%20phones%20and%20the%20WhatsApp%20history%20of%20people%20randomly%20to%20identify%20potential%20ganja%20addicts%20and%20sellers.%C2%A0%20These%20type%20of%20searches%20are%20still%20happening%20in%20the%20areas%20around%20Dhoolpet%2C%20Mangalhat%2C%20Bhoiguda%20Kaman%2C%20and%20Jumeraat%20Bazaar%2C%20etc.%20Protesting%20this%20extreme%20form%20of%20illegal%20policing%2C%20the%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Fhyd-police-commissioner-sent-legal-notice-over-random-whatsapp-checks-drugs-157073%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternet%20Freedom%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fins%3Ehad%20previously%20issued%20a%20legal%20notice%20to%20the%20then%20Hyderabad%20police%20commissioner%20and%20present%20state%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Anjani%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETNM%20has%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftopic%2Ftelangana-surveillance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20extensively%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%20about%20controversial%20police%20exercises%2C%20including%20cordon%20and%20search%2C%20which%20are%20justified%20as%20%E2%80%98preemptive%20measures%E2%80%99%20to%20prevent%20crime.%20The%20cordon%20and%20search%20operation%20involves%20blocking%20off%20an%20area%2C%20usually%20slums%20or%20localities%20that%20house%20poor%20people%2C%20and%20check%20for%20their%20Aadhaar%20card%2C%20gas%20cylinder%20and%20vehicle%20documents.%20Previously%20restricted%20to%20searches%20by%20the%20Army%20in%20conflict%20zones%2C%20this%20operation%20has%20now%20spread%20to%20states%20like%20Telanagna%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrisking%20people%20randomly%20is%20completely%20illegal.%20There%20should%20be%20some%20credible%20suspicion%20if%20such%20an%20action%20is%20being%20carried%20out.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20an%20FIR%20or%20a%20case%20registered%20in%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20General%20Diary.%20Without%20any%20credible%20evidence%2C%20searching%20people%20randomly%20is%20illegal%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20lawyer%20Vasudha%20Nagaraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20eateries%20that%20were%20searched%20on%20September%2016%20include%20King%20Khaja%20Hotel%2C%20Lucky%20Hotel%2C%20Hafeez%20Cafe%2C%20Mashallah%20Hotel%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20SHO%20Shiva%20Chandra%2C%20Santosh%20Nagar%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Muslim-populated%20area%2C%20has%20a%20problem%20with%20drugs%20and%20other%20criminal%20activities.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20%E2%80%98roadside%20romeos%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20suspects%20who%20sit%20in%20these%20eateries%20till%20late%20at%20night%20and%20plan%20crimes%20such%20as%20murder%2C%20smuggling%2C%20and%20other%20nefarious%20activities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20The%20policing%20is%20carried%20out%20only%20in%20the%20evenings%20and%20nights%20when%20there%20is%20heavy%20activity%2C%20he%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fpartner%2Fchildhood-cancer-why-advanced-paediatric-oncology-centres-are-key-to-saving-lives%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695204930000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20152945%2Fsantosh.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fillegal-lawyers-slam-hyderabad-cops-for-frisking-people-at-cafes-as-preventative-measure%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20September%2016%2C%20the%20Santosh%20Nagar%20police%20in%20Hyderabad%20carried%20out%20searches%20in%2010%20eateries%20and%20frisked%20all%20the%20customers%20for%20ganja%20and%20weapons.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fillegal-lawyers-slam-hyderabad-cops-for-frisking-people-at-cafes-as-preventative-measure%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Trump%20officials%20are%20already%20planning%20their%20White%20House%20return%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695204678000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103808821%2Cimgsize-131474.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fex-donald-trump-officials-are-already-planning-their-white-house-return%2Far