oved%20to%20the%20Northeastern%20state%20in%20search%20of%20a%20better%20life%20for%20his%20family.%20And%20he%20succeeded%20in%20his%20goals.%20Today%2C%20he%20lives%20in%20a%202%2C000-square-foot%2C%20four-bedroom%20house.%20He%20also%20supported%20his%20three%20younger%20siblings%E2%80%99%20education%20and%20marriage%2C%20making%20his%20parents%E2%80%99%20lives%20comfortable.%20He%20credits%20all%20his%20achievements%20to%20his%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20made%20sure%20that%20he%20gave%20all%20of%20us%20a%20good%20education.%20He%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20educate%20us%20and%20managed%20to%20pay%20all%20our%20fees%20by%20borrowing%20money%20and%20mortgaging%20jewellery.%20Three%20of%20my%20siblings%20are%20postgraduates%20and%20one%20has%20completed%20her%20doctorate.%20All%20of%20us%20are%20in%20good%20positions%20thanks%20to%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20on%20getting%20us%20educated%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nellayapan%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20humble%20beginnings%20to%20deputy%20director%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nellayapan%20B%2C%20OSD%20to%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330245%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENellayapan%20B%2C%20OSD%20to%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201990%2C%20Nellayapan%20had%20just%20completed%20an%20MSc%20in%20physics.%20His%20older%20sister%20was%20getting%20married%2C%20for%20which%20his%20parents%2C%20who%20ran%20a%20tea%2Fsnack%20stall%2C%20had%20to%20borrow%20money%20from%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20the%20time%20before%20my%20sister%E2%80%99s%20wedding.%20People%20refused%20to%20lend%20money.%20My%20parents%20managed%20the%20required%20money%20with%20great%20difficulty.%20Till%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20the%20moneylenders%20kept%20us%20hanging.%20I%20felt%20so%20insulted.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20resolved%20to%20achieve%20something%20big%20in%20life%2C%20so%20my%20parents%20would%20never%20have%20to%20face%20such%20a%20situation%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENellayapan%E2%80%99s%20college%20senior%2C%20who%20was%20working%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20apprised%20him%20about%20the%20opportunities%20there.%20And%20the%20then%2023-year-old%20left%20for%20Nagaland%20with%20Rs%202%2C000%20in%20his%20pocket%20and%20big%20dreams%20in%20his%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20me%20four%20days%20to%20reach%20Nagaland.%20My%20parents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327829%2Flilyma-khan-head-chef-at-dear-donna-delhi-shares-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecouldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20train%20ticket%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20mother%20had%20to%20pawn%20her%20last%20piece%20of%20jewellery%20%E2%80%94%20her%20nose%20ring%20%E2%80%94%20which%20got%20us%20Rs%202%2C000.%20I%20remember%20the%20bank%20manager%E2%80%99s%20expression%20when%20he%20saw%20the%20nose%20ring%2C%20knowing%20we%20had%20no%20other%20choice.%20I%20felt%20helpless%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20adding%20that%20the%20amount%20helped%20him%20with%20food%20and%20lodging%20for%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201991%2C%20he%20started%20his%20career%20as%20a%20private%20school%20teacher%20in%20Nagaland%20with%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month.%20He%20shares%20that%20this%20money%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20cover%20his%20expenses%20as%20he%20sent%20some%20money%20back%20home%20too.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20pay%20Rs%20700%20per%20month%20for%20electricity%20and%20rent.%20How%20could%20I%20survive%20on%20just%20Rs%20300%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20taking%20tuition%20for%20school%20students%20to%20supplement%20my%20income.%20I%20used%20to%20tutor%20from%206%20am%20to%2010%20am%2C%20then%20attend%20school%20until%204%20pm%2C%20and%20return%20to%20tutor%20again%20until%206%20pm.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20managed%20for%20the%20first%20six%20years%20in%20private%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20the%20time%20when%20Nagaland%20was%20facing%20insurgency%20issues.%20But%20the%20teacher%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20that%20hinder%20his%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20Nellayapan%20got%20a%20job%20as%20a%20postgraduate%20teacher%20in%20physics%20at%20the%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20in%20Dimapur.%20In%201999%2C%20he%20got%20married%20and%20remembers%20how%20they%20then%20put%20an%20asbestos%20roof%20on%20their%20house.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20burden%20of%20responsibility%20is%20often%20a%20blessing.%20I%20had%20to%20move%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20school%20principal%20in%202012%20and%20continued%20working%20there%20till%202017.%20Then%2C%20in%202018%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20assistant%20director%20at%20the%20Directorate%20of%20School%2